ReturnQueueEntryTest
public class SubmitQueueEntryTest
extends ConfigurableTest

If the message tested contains a JMF SubmitQueueEntry message, the JDF file referenced by the SubmitQueueEntry message (JMF/Message[@Type='SubmitQueueEntry']/QueueSubmissionParams/@URL) will be validated.

Author:
Claes Buckwalter (clabu@itn.liu.se)
